You will answer 20 questions about your Kids Mode UI design and output all results strictly in JSON.

Please respond in the following JSON structure:

{
  "model": "<your_model_name>",
  "kids_mode_answers": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "question": "<original question text>",
      "answer": "<your answer>"
    },
    ...
    {
      "id": 20,
      "question": "<original question text>",
      "answer": "<your answer>"
    }
  ]
}

Do NOT add explanations outside JSON. Only output JSON.
